high_descs: Go in the living room, and stand in front of the coffeetable and sofa.
Pick up the butterknife that is in front of you on the coffee table.
Walk around the coffee table on its right side, and face the tomato on the sofa.
Using the knife, cut the tomato that is on the sofa.
Walk to your left between the sofa and sidetable.
Put the butterknife down on the sidetable that is on the left side of the sofa.
Turn around and go back to standing in front of the sofa.
Pick up a thin middle slice of the tomato.
Walk with the tomato slice to the bowl in the kitchen sink.
Put the tomato slice in the bowl that is in the sink.
Pick up the bowl with the tomato in it.
Carry the bowl with the tomato in it to the microwave.
Open the microwave door, put the bowl and tomato in the microwave, and close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Microwave a middle tomato slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the coffeetable.
Take the butterknife from the table.
Turn around and go near the tomato.
Cut the tomato into pieces using the knife.
Turn around and go near the sidetable.
Put the butterknife on the sidetable.
Turn around and go near the sofa.
Take the tomato from the couch.
Turn around and go near the bowl.
Put the tomato into the bowl.
Take the bowl with tomato from the sink.
Turn around and go near the microwave.
Put the bowl with tomato into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Placed the Tomato into the Bowl and put it into the Microwave.

high_descs: make a left and go into the living room by the coffeetable.
pick up the butterknife from the coffee table.
walk around to the other side of the tomato and face the sofa.
Cut the tomato that is on the sofa.
walk to the end of the sidetable.
Put the butterknife on the sidetable.
turn around and walk to the sofa.
pick up the tomato from the sofa.
walk to the kitchen and put the tomato in the bowl in the sink.
Pick up the tomato from the bowl.
walk to the bowl.
open the door to the microwave.
Put the bowl in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Get the bowl from the living room and put in the microwave.
